elements.description: I want to add Suppliers with Multiple Data

steps.name: wait for username with "name" and "username" and "10"
wait for supplierlink with "xpath" and "(//a[contains(text(),'Suppliers')])[2]" and "10"
wait for AddIcon with "xpath" and "(//span[@data-caption='Add'])[1]" and "10"
wait for supplier number with "name" and "x_Supplier_Number" and "10"
Enter in "I am a new Supplier" with "xpath" and "//textarea[@id='x_Notes']"
wait for confirm OK button with "xpath" and "//button[normalize-space()='OK!']" and "10"
click confirm OK button with "xpath" and "//button[normalize-space()='OK!']"
wait for Alert OK button with "xpath" and "(//button[starts-with(text(),'OK')])[6]" and "10"
click for Alert OK button with "xpath" and "(//button[starts-with(text(),'OK')])[6]"
